option._queryString: {[c; m; op] select from option where ccy = c, maturity = m, option_type = op}

strike._queryString: {[c; m; op] select distinct strike from option where ccy = c, maturity = m, option_type = op}

symbol._queryString: {[c; m; op; s] select distinct sym from option where ccy = c, maturity = m, option_type = op, strike = s}

GetPosition._queryString: {[pid] update index: "-"{`$first x vs y}/: string sym from portfolio}

Ticker._queryString: {[s] `Time xcols () xkey (select Date: first date, Open: first price, High: max price, Low: min price, Close: last price, Volume: count sym by Time:`timestamp$(1 xbar time.minute + date) from future where sym = s)}

ETH._queryString: {[m] `c_sym`c_iv`c_ask`c_bid xcols () xkey (select c_sym:last sym, c_biv:last biv, c_bid:last bid, c_iv:last iv, c_aiv:last aiv, c_ask:last ask, c_delta: last delta by strike from option where maturity = m, ccy = `ETH, option_type =`C) ^ (select p_biv:last biv, p_bid:last bid, p_iv:last iv, p_aiv:last aiv, p_ask:last ask, p_delta: last delta, p_sym:last sym by strike from option where maturity = m, ccy = `ETH, option_type =`P)}

BTC._queryString: {[m] `c_sym`c_iv`c_ask`c_bid`c_aiv`c_biv`c_delta xcols () xkey (select c_sym:last sym, c_biv:last biv, c_bid:last bid, c_iv:last iv, c_aiv:last aiv, c_ask:last ask, c_delta: last delta by strike from option where maturity = m, ccy = `BTC, option_type =`C) ^ (select p_biv:last biv, p_bid:last bid, p_iv:last iv, p_aiv:last aiv, p_ask:last ask, p_delta: last delta, p_sym:last sym by strike from option where maturity = m, ccy =`BTC, option_type =`P)}
